data.title: CCPS Registration Central
data.meta_description: CCPS Registration Central  - Clayton County Public Schools
data.text: Registration for the 2024-2025 school year for students who did not attend a Clayton County Public School in 2023-2024 is now open. Parents have unlimited access to the online registration application. It is available 24 hours a day, seven days a week, and 365 days a year. Prior to beginning the online application, please view the videos below. Online registration for the 2024-2025 school year is as easy as 1, 2, 3! Before you being to complete the Online Registration Application, OLR, please be sure and view the tutorial video below.
